Mileage varies for everyone of course, but in my case one canister lasts me about a month or so with my sodastream source. For me it’s worth the $15 for the exchange but in others cases it could be different. If anything just take note of the equipment used for filling.

The reason why you should get the exchanges is because the equipment used to fill them are medical grade; ie no unwanted foreign particles whereas other equipment isn’t certified for that. I’d be extremely wary of the equipment used for filling if I were you.
